  As I am not an enchanter(or enchantress for that mater!), I have only a limited knowledge of how the mezzes work.  I am wondering why it seems that some mobs just don't get mezzed, or will only hold the mez for a limited time...<br>
  I have heard that charisma affects this, does anyone know how much?  Do the mobs gets mezzed and then break it if you don't have enough charisma? <br>
<br>
   If you can shed some light on my ignorance, I'd greatly appreciate it.<br>
<br>
